<title>Thepna Luipi Lien!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Phat a kidang vaihawmna ni lopi,
 Ni chengin ka naih zel;
 Thepna leh lungkham buoina hi,
 Ka dogal chu a hung lien ie.

[V2]
 Kei maiin ei umsak kin,
 Ka kawmah um zelin;
 Zion tang hawih ka tun ma chun,
 Ka Hukdampa ei pui zelin.

[V3]
 2. Ka maah thepna luipi ahung lien,
 Beihmang ka lau Lalpa;
 Zie luipi a tum mangte chu,
 Kumsawt gam tungta hiel puona.

[V4]
 3. Nova damlai a thil umzie bangin,
 Leh Sodom khuo bangin;
 Amauhaw nawpsak ngaihtuohna'n,
 Aw Lalpa a kihei zo tau.

[V5]
 4. Na lehkhabu thienga zik mah bangin,
 Khawvel hi a buoi tai;
 Hehpihna a hung dai zo tai,
 Buoina leh lungkham na'n a dim.

[V6]
 5. Khawvel gimtheihna leh lungkhamna hin,
 Pa mel ei muhsak in;
 Zion chate nawptatna ding,
 Ni lopi chu a nai ta ie.</lyrics>
</song>